---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <section style="background:white;padding:5rem 1.5rem;">
    <div style="max-width:80rem;margin:0 auto;">

      <div id="about-grid">

        <!-- Text -->
        <div>
          <p style="font-size:0.875rem;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#2563eb;">About Jake</p>
          <h2 style="margin-top:0.75rem;font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:800;color:#111827;line-height:1.2;">
            A Lifelong Passion for Fixing Things
          </h2>
          <p style="margin-top:1.25rem;line-height:1.75;color:#4b5563;font-size:1.05rem;">
            Hi, I'm Jake. I've been passionate about technology since I was a kid — taking things apart, figuring out how they work and putting them back together. What started as a hobby turned into a career, and over the past 10 years I've built up real hands-on experience repairing computers, consoles and all kinds of tech.
          </p>
          <p style="margin-top:1rem;line-height:1.75;color:#4b5563;font-size:1.05rem;">
            Over the past 10 years I've turned that lifelong passion into real experience — repairing computers, consoles and all kinds of tech for friends, family and customers. I recently launched Jake Fixes Tech LLC right here in Littleton, NH to bring affordable, honest tech repair to my community.
          </p>
          <p style="margin-top:1rem;line-height:1.75;color:#4b5563;font-size:1.05rem;">
            When your tech isn't working I know how stressful that can be. I'm here to make the process as smooth and painless as possible — no upselling, no confusing jargon, just honest work at a fair price.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Values -->
        <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1.5rem;">

          <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;">
            <div style="display:flex;height:2.75rem;width:2.75rem;flex-shrink:0;align-items:center;justify-content:center;border-radius:0.5rem;background:#dbeafe;color:#2563eb;">
              <svg style="height:1.25rem;width:1.25rem;" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 style="font-weight:600;color:#111827;">Passion for Tech</h3>
              <p style="margin-top:0.25rem;font-size:0.875rem;line-height:1.625;color:#4b5563;">Been tinkering with computers and gadgets since childhood and never stopped. Every repair is a puzzle I genuinely love solving.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;">
            <div style="display:flex;height:2.75rem;width:2.75rem;flex-shrink:0;align-items:center;justify-content:center;border-radius:0.5rem;background:#dbeafe;color:#2563eb;">
              <svg style="height:1.25rem;width:1.25rem;" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="6"/><path d="M15.477 12.89L17 22l-5-3-5 3 1.523-9.11"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 style="font-weight:600;color:#111827;">Honest Service</h3>
              <p style="margin-top:0.25rem;font-size:0.875rem;line-height:1.625;color:#4b5563;">No upselling, no hidden fees. You get a clear diagnosis and fair price before any work begins. If it can't be fixed I'll tell you straight.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;">
            <div style="display:flex;height:2.75rem;width:2.75rem;flex-shrink:0;align-items:center;justify-content:center;border-radius:0.5rem;background:#dbeafe;color:#2563eb;">
              <svg style="height:1.25rem;width:1.25rem;" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 style="font-weight:600;color:#111827;">Community First</h3>
              <p style="margin-top:0.25rem;font-size:0.875rem;line-height:1.625;color:#4b5563;">Proud to serve Littleton, NH and the surrounding North Country — homes, families and small businesses that deserve tech support they can trust.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  #about-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 3rem;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    #about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      align-items: center;
    }
  }
</style>